How to Keep Your Glass Tumblers Sparkling! ✨🥤

Want your glass can tumbler to stay looking brand new? Here’s how to clean it properly! 💖 Hand wash with mild soap and warm water, avoid abrasive sponges, and let it air dry.

Remember, no dishwasher or soaking to protect the design. Keep your tumbler fresh and ready for your favorite drinks! 💦✨
